Build a Complete Somalia Bajaj & Motorcycle Ride-Hailing Application

Create a modern, production-ready ride-hailing mobile and web platform designed specifically for Somalia. The application should work like Uber/Bolt but focus mainly on Bajaj (Tuk-Tuk) and Motorcycle transportation.

The system should connect passengers with nearby Bajaj and Motorcycle drivers using GPS, maps, and real-time ride requests.

---

